msgid "\n"
"        Set the action for the bot to take when NoNuke is triggered\n\n"
"        **Actions**\n"
"        `kick` - kick the user\n"
"        `ban` - ban the user\n"
"        `strip` - strip all roles with permissions from user\n"
"        `notify` - just sends a report to the log channel\n"
"        "
